through mine.

47:51.954 --> 47:53.246
Well, are you sure
it's the equipment?

47:53.247 --> 47:54.747
What do you mean?

47:54.748 --> 47:57.416
Well, I'm not getting
anything on this, either.

47:57.417 --> 47:59.126
What do you mean? What's wrong?

47:59.127 --> 48:00.962
What's wrong?

48:00.963 --> 48:03.590
It's all right. We just need
to double check a couple things.

48:13.809 --> 48:15.978
