- No pulse.

48:16.728 --> 48:19.146
Well, what do you mean,
"No blood pressure, no pulse"?

48:19.147 --> 48:20.815
Shh. Take it easy. Take it easy.

48:20.816 --> 48:22.359
[beeping]

48:28.490 --> 48:30.449
- What do you have?
- 70.

48:30.450 --> 48:32.118
- 70 what?
- 70 degrees.

48:32.119 --> 48:34.830
- Well, what's that?
- Room temperature.

48:36.331 --> 48:38.417
Come over here for a second.
I want to talk to you.

48:40.794 --> 48:42.379
[whispers]

48:44.590 --> 48:46.091
What are you guys saying?

48:46.884 --> 48:48.385
What are you guys saying?

48:48.594 --> 48:49.887
[ Pounding on the door ]

48:50.095 --> 48:51.721
What was that thing down there?

48:51.722 --> 48:54.223
- What the fuck are we gonna do?
- Hey, Suicide's down there.

48:54.224 --> 48:56.851
No way man, he's gone.
That thing ate his head.

48:56.852 --> 48:58.103
Jesus!

48:59.646 --> 49:01.230
I don't hear anything
down there, do you?

49:01.231 --> 49:02.690
Oh, we got to call somebody.

49:02.691 --> 49:04.817
- Who?
- The cops.

49:04.818 --> 49:07.695
I don't wanna call no cop.
The cops are just gonna kick our ass.

49:07.696 --> 49:09.655
Just let's get out of here, okay?

49:09.656 --> 49:11.616
No! We gotta call somebody.

49:11.617 --> 49:13.868
Wait a minute, where's Freddy?

49:13.869 --> 49:15.954
He was gone, he wasn't here
when I showed up.

49:32.220 --> 49:33.931
[thunder claps]

49:39.227 --> 49:42.104
Holy shit. We're gonna have
to swim to get over there.

49:42.105 --> 49:44.357
[strange moaning]

49:44.358 --> 49:46.025
What the fuck was that?

49:46.026 --> 49:48.153
Look! There!

49:49.529 --> 49:51.323
[thunder claps]

