50:33.115 --> 50:34.908
No! No!

50:38.912 --> 50:41.580
You have no pulse, your blood
pressure's zero over zero,

50:41.581 --> 50:43.124
you have no pupillary response,

50:43.125 --> 50:45.210
no reflexes, your
temperature is 70 degrees.

50:47.713 --> 50:49.213
W-what does that mean?

50:49.214 --> 50:52.758
It's a puzzle, because technically,
you're not alive.

50:52.759 --> 50:55.636
Except you're conscious, so
we don't know what it means.

50:55.637 --> 50:58.305
- Are you saying we're dead?
- Let's not jump to conclusions.

50:58.306 --> 51:01.475
Obviously, I didn't mean
you were really dead.

51:01.476 --> 51:03.811
Dead people don't move
around and talk.

51:03.812 --> 51:04.937
[banging]

51:04.938 --> 51:07.023
- What's the hell's that?
- Front door.

51:07.024 --> 51:09.650
- What the fuck are they doing?
- I'll find out.

51:09.651 --> 51:11.610
Listen we're gonna go
get a couple of stretchers.

51:11.611 --> 51:13.612
Just hang in there.
W-we won't be a second.

51:13.613 --> 51:14.822
[girl screams]

51:14.823 --> 51:16.157
Open the door.

51:16.158 --> 51:17.450
Open the door, please.

51:17.451 --> 51:18.451
Help!

51:18.452 --> 51:20.120
Hey! Open the door!

51:21.371 --> 51:22.747
Open the door!

51:22.748 --> 51:25.375
Hurry up!

51:26.626 --> 51:28.169
Freeze, or you're dead!

51:28.170 --> 51:29.545
Don't shoot, man!

51:29.546 --> 51:31.797
Are you crazy? Are you on PCP?

51:31.798 --> 51:33.924
None of us are on any
drugs, man. Just let us in!

51:33.925 --> 51:36.052
All right, come in, come in.
But no funny moves.

51:36.053 --> 51:37.386
Shit, no.

51:37.387 --> 51:39.138
You gotta lock all your
doors and your windows,

51:39.139 --> 51:40.598
and call the cops!
They're out there!

51:40.599 --> 51:42.433
- What? Who's out there?
- Don't you hear that?

51:42.434 --> 51:45.019
- What?
- Shut up and listen, man!

51:45.020 --> 51:46.980
[distant screaming and moaning]

51:47.439 --> 51:48.647
What is it?

51:48.648 --> 51:51.358
- It's dead people screaming.
- What dead people?

51:51.359 --> 51:52.860
They came from out of the ground.

51:52.861 --> 51:53.903
And they're after us.

51:53.904 --> 51:55.654
Out of the ground?

51:55.655 --> 51:58.365
Our friends took off the other way.
And they're out there now!

51:58.366 --> 52:00.868
[corpses moan]

52:00.869 --> 52:03.955
Brains!

52:04.998 --> 52:07.000
Brains!

52:07.918 --> 52:09.586
Brains!

52:10.420 --> 52:12.047
Brains!

52:14.174 --> 52:17.176
- Trash? Where's Trash?
- Didn't she go with them?

52:17.177 --> 52:19.096
I thought she was with us.

52:21.473 --> 52:23.433
- Hey, do you hear that?
- Hear what?

52:24.142 --> 52:25.936
[screaming and moaning]

52:26.269 --> 52:27.813
Christ, Jesus.

52:28.480 --> 52:29.980
What is that?

52:29.981 --> 52:31.900
It sounds like people screaming.

52:32.567 --> 52:35.445
You get the stretchers,
I'll get on the radio and phone this in.

52:45.789 --> 52:47.499
[starts engine]

52:51.795 --> 52:53.255
[screams]

52:55.882 --> 52:57.342
Jerry?

53:00.929 --> 53:02.347
[screams]

53:03.807 --> 53:05.057
[screams]

53:05.058 --> 53:06.767
Brain!

53:06.768 --> 53:08.937
Brain! Brain!

53:10.480 --> 53:12.148
What? What kind of a problem?

53:12.149 --> 53:13.732
Take a look at it.

53:13.733 --> 53:15.860
Why, what the hell's
going on out here?

53:15.861 --> 53:17.695
That graveyard out
there's full of people

53:17.696 --> 53:19.071
coming out of the ground.

53:19.072 --> 53:20.531
Whaddya mean "out of the ground"?

53:20.532 --> 53:22.158
Yes, out of the ground.

53:22.159 --> 53:24.451
They're horrible, they scream,
you've got to do something.

53:24.452 --> 53:25.452
Scream--?

53:25.453 --> 53:26.954
Yes, mister, they're out there.

53:26.955 --> 53:28.956
And there's one of them
in that warehouse.

53:28.957 --> 53:31.333
- Which-- which warehouse?
- The medical supply house.

53:31.334 --> 53:33.377
Oh, shit! Shit!

53:33.378 --> 53:34.712
- And they're--
- Goddamn!

53:34.713 --> 53:37.339
I-I-I think things are
getting out of hand.

53:37.340 --> 53:40.092
Mister, there's 100 of
those things out there.

53:40.093 --> 53:41.385
100?

53:41.386 --> 53:43.012
The cops. We got to call the cops.

53:43.013 --> 53:45.347
Yeah. No shit.

53:45.348 --> 53:48.601
Phone. Where the fuck is the phone?

53:48.602 --> 53:50.395
There! There's an office!

53:55.400 --> 53:57.861
Hello, operator, give me the police.
This is an emergency.

53:59.696 --> 54:01.198
[screams]

54:04.367 --> 54:07.204
Grab the hammer and nails! Casey!

54:08.038 --> 54:11.081
Quiet! Let's just get the
hell out of here, Ernie.

54:11.082 --> 54:13.125
- You got a car?
- I got a car.

54:13.126 --> 54:14.752
Get your keys.
Let's get out of here.

54:14.753 --> 54:16.337
My clutch is shot.

54:16.338 --> 54:18.215
We'll use the paramedic ambulance.

54:19.257 --> 54:20.382
Freddy! Oh!

54:20.383 --> 54:21.926
- Ernie?
- Yeah?

54:21.927 --> 54:23.510
Where are the paramedics?

54:23.511 --> 54:25.387
I'll get them.
Get my own car started.

54:25.388 --> 54:27.849
Oh, my god, Freddy!
What did they do to you?

54:59.422 --> 55:01.341
[screams]

55:01.591 --> 55:03.510
[screams]

55:10.809 --> 55:13.310
- Oh, God!
- What was that shooting?

55:13.311 --> 55:15.271
- Oh, God!
- What? What, Ernie?

55:15.272 --> 55:16.231
God!

55:17.399 --> 55:20.109
- Oh, God!
- What the hell?

55:20.110 --> 55:21.528
It...

55:21.861 --> 55:23.113
It!

55:23.989 --> 55:26.198
"It"? It what? What is "it"?

55:26.199 --> 55:28.742
They're all over the cars.

55:28.743 --> 55:32.288
It's horrible.
They're out there. They're...

55:32.289 --> 55:36.542
Paramedics are dead. And we--we
can't take the cars. We-- I‒ Burt,

55:36.543 --> 55:39.628
we've gotta--we've
gotta call the police.

55:39.629 --> 55:41.588
Set him down. Set him down.

55:41.589 --> 55:43.049
Set him down. Easy.

55:44.259 --> 55:46.845
It's not--not--not
it's not working.

55:47.304 --> 55:48.513
Come on.

56:06.573 --> 56:08.657
- What's the matter?
- Dead.

56:08.658 --> 56:09.992
[glass breaking]

56:09.993 --> 56:12.078
Brains! Brains!

56:20.587 --> 56:22.172
Help me.

