59:24.062 --> 59:26.855
First, I got a really fucked headache.

59:26.856 --> 59:31.151
Then--then my--my stomach
started cramping--cramping up.

59:31.152 --> 59:33.488
Now my arms and legs are cramping.

59:34.906 --> 59:36.698
Let's take a look. Let's take a look.

59:36.699 --> 59:38.116
[cracking sound]

59:38.117 --> 59:39.660
Oh, God!

59:39.661 --> 59:41.078
[screams]

59:41.079 --> 59:43.872
Let's get his shirt up, huh?

59:43.873 --> 59:45.374
What are you doing, Ernie?

59:45.375 --> 59:47.417
Oh, God.

59:47.418 --> 59:50.254
Uh, the bruises where he's lying down,

59:50.255 --> 59:51.922
uh,

59:51.923 --> 59:54.091
