59:54.092 --> 59:55.677
[cracking]

59:56.135 --> 59:58.263
Easy. Easy. Easy!

59:59.847 --> 01:00:01.140
Okay.

01:00:05.353 --> 01:00:07.437
You know, it looks like

01:00:07.438 --> 01:00:09.439
